- Levantar o ambiente
docker-compose up -d

- Parar o ambiente
docker-compose stop

- Matar os containers do projeto
docker-compose down

- Instalar dependencias do Composer:
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "composer install"

- Gerar chave do App:
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan key:generate"

- Executa as migrations
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan migrate"

- Apagar todas migrations
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan migrate:refresh --seed"

- Gerar autoload da aplicação
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "composer dump-autoload"

- Popular as primeiras tabelas do sistema
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan db:seed"

- Criar storage link para armazenar os arquivos anexos
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan storage:link"

- Limpar cache de configuração
docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan config:clear"

docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "php artisan --version"

docker exec -ti app-matic sh -c "composer require doctrine/dbal"
